# Supabase Boundary

- Import client only via `@/shared/api/supabase` or `@gridix/utils/api`.
- Use generated DB types from `@gridix/types/database`.
- Keep TanStack Query keys explicit and namespaced (e.g. `["projects", id, "editor"]`).
